<h4 id="asthimo-ii">Asthimo II</h4>
<p>Asthimo II was the final iteration of Asthimo 0, which had the rounded shape rather than the square, box shape. The overall shape of the robot stayed the same, although the robot head was rounder and less flat on top. The antenna shape shape and design remained mostly the same, although I believe we decreased the length slightly so that the antennae wouldnâ€™t stick up as far. Instead of having the facial features extruded from the face, the features are at an equal level with the rest of the face, making the entire consistent across.</p>

