<h2 id="design-board">Design Board</h2>
<p>Our design board drew inspiration from the design of old science fiction magazines - such as Analog Science Fiction and Fact, Asimovâ€™s Science Fiction, Galaxy, Amazing Stories, etc. We made sure to highlight all of the key features of Asthimo such as the spacer and the modular customizable design, as well as important information such as dimensions, intended age range, and the warning disclaimer to remove the arms and accessories before use. We decided to use Asthimo II on the cover of the magazine, since they look the most like a rounded Asimovian robot - such as those from I, Robot or Robot Visions.</p>

